{"tid":2500250,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解美式曲奇咁好食","createTime":"2021-04-22T13:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T13:45:46.000Z","uid":182683,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"360fec35c3d6cef5ced5bd57dc5ccc733ee0103f","tid":2500250,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"美式朱古力曲奇真係好屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n軟得黎有啲咬口 跟住啲朱古力流心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個食譜我試左好多唔同比例 食到喉嚨痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過真係好多糖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間唔中下午茶食一塊已經變肥仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係食完一塊又想繼續食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sEj-mu13jXg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsEj-mu13jXg&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=9181a497\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sEj-mu13jXg</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNwSVRRfiyZSDeKdv7StsyGGX62cg39d3KSNusUzvxTcH?filename=MywUyKx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMywUyKx.png&h=9314edb0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmePFYUoXaFoERSqyGS2zdHp12a21tNXwbkEvBstnfdEWe?filename=yUEu64y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyUEu64y.jpg&h=87b8abf4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPrJG4gi9QB89ZqbkNxH6NmVXgwFbnJLpvuqNVgzyMmhd?filename=k1L2HCV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1L2HCV.jpg&h=f0e0becd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZZtQ6RNgGNN9Z9Edv7wNVdN1H8vGcuvtSXYeWoqgFKqH?filename=RyF964B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRyF964B.jpg&h=5f4b0c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http